{"tid":1185202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜五月主張恢復軍公教年金(片)  但今日4/6韓發「聲明」 指從未主張過恢復軍公教18％年金","createTime":"2019-06-04T06:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T10:20:12.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e687f581a27427594bf5ee3efcedd25efac1d14e","tid":1185202,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜發「聲明」 指從未主張恢復軍公教18％年金<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-04<br />\n<br />\n〔記者王榮祥／高雄報導〕針對部分媒體甚至名嘴錯誤指述，高雄市長韓國主張恢復軍公教18%年金，<span style=\"color: red;\">韓國瑜今發4點聲明鄭重澄清，從未主張恢復軍公教18%年金，呼籲惡意扭曲人士不要再刻意抹黑。</span><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜4點聲明：<br />\n<br />\n1. 政府不能失信於民。韓國瑜關注的是程序正義，公教人員在考取公職時即代表相關福利保障。<br />\n<br />\n2. 應尊重法律體制。明明公教制度已有法定機關銓敘部規範，當然要尊重制度，不該以國家年金改革委員會或其他組織任意取代。<br />\n<br />\n3. 年金的管理效能應提高。新加坡的年金基金管理獲利率是6%,台灣只有2%，明顯還有管理效能提升的空間。<br />\n<br />\n4. 政府不能債留子孫。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2811545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2811545&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9Cggmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=cd43546d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2811545&h=dc2d8934\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2811545</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_35VP9qYEic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_35VP9qYEic&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9Cggmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=4df05f3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_35VP9qYEic</a><br />\n20190530中天新聞　軍公教年改　韓國瑜主張恢復政府承諾"},{"pid":"649f053b4bb1b11badded3bfbdb60774e27852f0","tid":1185202,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab8727764a8f706145c274000cf27452ab011c8","tid":1185202,"uid":254183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bFwFzcH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbFwFzcH.jpg&h=35b77b95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2230ab7dc55716f1b28fe5d663509b305440274","tid":1185202,"uid":81345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:32:20.000Z","msg":"(他在)高雄發大財"},{"pid":"6368a9acd1bb29178a83bb53d046e9f749c9f951","tid":1185202,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:33:04.000Z","msg":"1/6參加韓國瑜總統造勢大會<br />\n淋雨嗰批軍公教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527a07184b32abef3ab6a4750b84863480cfb2b6","tid":1185202,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:33:35.000Z","msg":"18%年金真係CLS！"},{"pid":"fa99e056118b025d56f636624994d223386dd920","tid":1185202,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6368a9acd1bb29178a83bb53d046e9f749c9f951","tid":1185202,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:33:04.000Z","msg":"1/6參加韓國瑜總統造勢大會<br />\n淋雨嗰批軍公教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:34:26.000Z","msg":"但台狗照樣係會投票比韓國瑜<br />\n<br />\n台灣已END GAME, 無得救了"},{"pid":"ddd8252b1cc6b6d0b211eb46dea3698734a4005a","tid":1185202,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"527a07184b32abef3ab6a4750b84863480cfb2b6","tid":1185202,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:33:35.000Z","msg":"18%年金真係CLS！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:37:27.000Z","msg":"國民黨都支持修改年金<br />\n有提出自己國民黨方案<br />\n最後立法院通過了民進黨方案"},{"pid":"2a55fa6813b71563c781385d76e1950db7c77257","tid":1185202,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ab8727764a8f706145c274000cf27452ab011c8","tid":1185202,"uid":254183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bFwFzcH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum